    <item>
      <title>新西兰在减肥药试验取得初步成功后将扩大试验范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/zealand-to-broaden-trial-of-weight-loss-drug-after-early-success</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在早期试验中显示出积极结果后，Zealand Pharma A/S 计划推进对一种潜在新型减肥药的更广泛研究，以与 Novo Nordisk A/S 和 Eli Lilly &amp; Co. 的治疗药物进行竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/zealand-to-broaden-trial-of-weight-loss-drug-after-early-success</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 16:41:31 GMT</pubDate>
